{"tid":2337541,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"政府記者會聲稱疫苗致敏率為百萬分之一","createTime":"2020-12-23T10:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T13:22:07.000Z","uid":38861,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"48212f64a18caa5b59bf1a52e47436c962844b59","tid":2337541,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"許樹昌教授在記者會中，引述美國注射疫苗時只有六宗過敏反應個案，且引述普遍數據過敏反應的機率為百萬分之一。<br />\n<br />\n參照美國原有資料(Ref1,Slide4)，過敏反應的而且確至少只有六宗個案，唯注射人士數量只有二十七萬，機率遠高於百萬分之一。<br />\n<br />\n隨著注射數量增加，機率不排除會調回至接近百萬分之一，但在現實例子與數據引用的差異上，政府專家們有必要主動指出，才能夠獲取市民的信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/acip/meetings/downloads/slides-2020-12/slides-12-19/05-COVID-CLARK.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fvaccines%2Facip%2Fmeetings%2Fdownloads%2Fslides-2020-12%2Fslides-12-19%2F05-COVID-CLARK.pdf&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=013afe83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/acip/meetings/downloads/slides-2020-12/slides-12-19/05-COVID-CLARK.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"8e780d9447eb637bae036c9755d8292bd0b8db75","tid":2337541,"uid":205339,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"Follow左樓主好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1be6b8c1e9e0c443354840a1b86cd822ace2ad","tid":2337541,"uid":34119,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"許樹昌鳩噏呃人非第一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd581818a179b736292165e0b1e05cbef970b261","tid":2337541,"uid":35301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"6&divide;270000 =1/45000"},{"pid":"5f8b76821dc9775215b473fb4f5c423e923ed771","tid":2337541,"uid":38861,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be1be6b8c1e9e0c443354840a1b86cd822ace2ad","tid":2337541,"uid":34119,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"cited